title: Phelim Comerford
text:
Phelim Comerford (birth unknown) is an Irish former professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who played in the 1990s. He played at representative level for <a href="Ireland%20national%20rugby%20league%20team">Ireland</a>, and at club level for <a href="Rugby%20League%20Ireland%23Teams%20in%20past%20seasons%20of%20the%20league">Dublin Blues</a>, as a .
International honours.
Comerford won 5 caps for <a href="Ireland%20national%20rugby%20league%20team">Ireland</a> in 1995–1997 while at Dublin Blues.
